{"tid":53854,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"上雪山用，timberland, columbia之外有冇平d既牌子","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T05:23:10.000Z","uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db4341fbdfbfc11fb16fb260563ba9fab88d01e4","tid":53854,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"上雪山睇雪<br />\n<br />\n外套columbia要千零蚊，其實咁大件都合理 但係好日都唔會用，見依家千色leaveland有6舊幾既，買果D會唔會好D? <br />\n <br />\n鞋既話， timber休閒果D 幾舊但係應該要高筒果對?<br />\n千幾蚊幾貴下，有冇D平D推介<br />\n<br />\nthanks thanks"},{"pid":"ed24860812d56f7a9a73a3b0f596b88576d0dc2a","tid":53854,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔應該係踢拖去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真你都去得雪山睇雪慳果幾舊做咩啫"},{"pid":"ba77edcb339f91f4954592674c37c7ef2cca9bdc","tid":53854,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:51:58.000Z","msg":"上雪山千零蚊點夠呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千零蚊貨仔出街著就得"},{"pid":"d460769a6773c98e7829221cb0532bebaa28c00d","tid":53854,"uid":858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"有啲錢無得慳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128879ea0d01e53735fe66ee41589fe3e853f97a","tid":53854,"uid":3208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲錢無得慳架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger 樓主唔好慳  columbia可以執齊成套雪山裝 你預坐底4，5千。基本野就速乾底衫，雪褲雪厚嬲，雪鞋。其他覺得自己要用就買，身體強壯以上都夠哂。"},{"pid":"dfe09db1db7157a71a5521822519edb3a797ce32","tid":53854,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"去留意下d 行山牌子<br />\n會抵玩過columbia 好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3987a06ac64d7e52cf64b861a9c604cb71681db0","tid":53854,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:56:35.000Z","m